  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nShe _____ a delicious cake for the party.\u00a0\n\nA. Baked\u00a0\nB. Boiled\u00a0\nC. Fried\u00a0\nD. Roasted\u00a0\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\nA\u00a0Explanation: \n\n\"Baked\" means to cook something in an oven, and is often used in reference to desserts like cakes.",
